title: 254. Andy, Carlos Reyes, Sal & DJ CTI: Women Of The Year, Congress Receives Raise & US Warns China
itunes:title: 254. Andy, Carlos Reyes, Sal & DJ CTI: Women Of The Year, Congress Receives Raise & US Warns China
description: In today's episode, Andy and the crew a joined in the studio by Carlos Reyes. They discuss openly transgender government official Rachel Levin being nominated as one of USA Today's Women of the year, Congress giving its staffers a 21% pay raise with the Omnibus Bill, and the US sending a warning to China to not assist Russia with the invasion of Ukraine.
